'Resi!'

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:02.800
'Tinggalkan dia!'

00:21:03.320 --> 00:21:04.920
'Resi!  Resi!'

00:21:05.840 --> 00:21:07.240
'Tinggalkan dia!  Resi!'

